# Personal samples and any decoded copy of them may contain secrets.
# The 20 public samples (samples/*.shortcut) decode to
# samples/decoded/*.xml and are checked in — they're Apple gallery
# shortcuts with no secrets. samples/private/ and samples/decoded/private/
# stay ignored.
samples/decoded/private/
samples/private/
*.shortcut.bplist
*.shortcut.xml
